1. *Čarli* je jutros rano ustao uz zoru. (Charlie got up early this morning at dawn.)
2. *Čarlima* je bilo zanimljivo da posete muzej. (Charlie's were interested in visiting the museum.)
3. Ona je svojim *čarlijem* donela poklon. (She brought a gift for her Charlie.)
4. *Čarliu* je trebalo više vremena da knjigu pročita. (Charlie needed more time to read the book.)
5. Ona je bila uzbuđena kada je videla *čarlija*. (She was excited when she saw Charlie.)